data.description: WATCH ME! and SHOW ME!  Nestled in the peaceful Sawgrass Bay neighborhood, this charming home is tucked away in a cul-de-sac, offering a tranquil retreat from the hustle and bustle. Recently updated, it boasts a brand-new roof and state-of-the-art AC system, providing both reliability and energy efficiency. The 2022 appliances and fresh paint lend a modern touch, creating a welcoming atmosphere. One of the standout features of this home is the wide open space downstairs, "Bonus Room", the upgraded stairs make an impressive reception for your visitors! Upstairs the master bedroom is completed with a balcony that offers a picturesque view of the adjacent orange groves. With no rear neighbors, this vantage point provides a serene backdrop for relaxation and enjoyment. Two additional bedrooms upstairs with walk-in closets share a convenient Jack and Jill bathroom, Great for sharing! Laundry room in the hallway! The thoughtful layout of the home caters to both functionality and comfort. An additional room downstairs adds versatility to the home and offers endless possibilities for customization, whether it be for a dedicated workspace, a cozy guest room, or a bonus recreational area. The Sawgrass Bay neighborhood offers a host of amenities, including a refreshing pool for cooling off on sunny days, scenic walking paths for leisurely strolls, a playground for the little ones, and a beach volleyball court for active recreation. This well-rounded community ensures that there's always something for everyone to enjoy right at your doorstep. In summary, this updated cul-de-sac home in Sawgrass Bay is a true gem, with its modern features, spacious layout, and idyllic location overlooking orange groves. The neighborhood is located just 25 minutes away from Disney! And will soon be connected through western way ,Winter Garden-Disney. Location! Olympus Sport Campus!!!
